    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Fanatical Pale Maw cultists driven by absolute faith in entropy doctrine. They dress in torn grey and silver robes, bearing self-inflicted ritual scars. Less disciplined than veterans but more dangerous when cornered. They fight without self-preservation instinct.</p>",
      "director": "<p><strong>ABILITIES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Entropy Weapon</strong> (Main, Melee, Might): T1 2 dmg; T2 5 dmg; T3 7 dmg.</li><li><strong>Zealous Cry</strong> (Main, Area 20ft, Presence, 1M): T1 1 psychic; T2 2 psychic + Presence test or frightened EoNT; T3 3 psychic + frightened EoNT all in range.</li></ul><p><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul><li><strong>True Believer:</strong> Immune to fear and charm. Cannot be demoralized.</li><li><strong>Martyr’s Rush:</strong> If another PM creature is reduced to 0 SP within 30ft, may immediately shift 3 squares toward the target as a free triggered action.</li><li><strong>Frenzied Devotion:</strong> Below half SP, +1 to all attacks and saves.</li></ul><p><strong>TACTICS:</strong> Rush melee targets. Use Zealous Cry against clustered enemies. Prioritize getting adjacent to Kaelen.</p>",
